data.description: This is the one! With over 27 acres and two charming houses this property has so much potential! The main house on the property has been nicely renovated with new appliances and an updated look throughout. The second home is perfect to use as a rental or mother-in-law suit. A small pond is on the property and a detached outbuilding with connected trailer that have its own HVAC system and is perfect for the man cave you dream about having! The property is cleared and well maintained and offers the opportunity for gardening, chickens or horses in the future (dream big!). If you are looking for the opportunity to build your forever home this is what you have been waiting for, do not miss out!
